A punchcard which can manage different tasks

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -s task, --start task
                        starts the timer for the task
  -p task / number, --pause task / number
                        stops the timer for the task
  -v task / number, --view task / number
                        view the detailed informations of a task
  -r task / number, --remove task / number
                        removes a task from the list
  -t task / number, --time task / number
                        total time of a task
  -x task / number, --status task / number
                        status of the task
  -l, --list            show a list of all tasks